---
title: Middle Eastern Style Prawn Stew with Chickpeas, Charred Courgette and Spiced Bulgur
description: This delicious Middle Eastern Style Prawn Stew has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-style-prawn-stew-f6ba8031-28801ebc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/middle-eastern-style-prawn-stew-620a1265a15db81cf01d3fbb-fd227127.pdf
author: Michael Steadman
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/middle-eastern-style-prawn-stew-620a1265a15db81cf01d3fbb
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Middle Eastern
nutrition:
  calories: 601 kcal
  fat: 14.9 g
